ZH: 我的妹妹是一名留学生，在加拿大学习医学。
EN: My younger sister is a foreign student studying medicine in Canada.

ZH: 大学里有很多留学生，来自不同的国家。
EN: There are many foreign exchange students in the university, coming from different countries.

ZH: 我们学校鼓励留学生参加各种文化交流活动。
EN: Our school encourages foreign students to participate in various cultural exchange activities.

ZH: 张老师是我们学校的留学生辅导员。
EN: Teacher Zhang is the foreign student advisor at our school.

ZH: 留学生在中国的生活费比较低。
EN: Living expenses for foreign students in China are relatively low.

ZH: 我们学校为留学生提供中文教学课程。
EN: Our school offers Chinese language classes for foreign students.

ZH: 留学生需要办理签证才能来中国留学。
EN: Foreign students need to apply for a visa to study in China.

ZH: 学校宿舍专门为留学生准备了单独的楼层。
EN: The school dormitory has a separate floor dedicated to foreign students.

ZH: 为了适应中国的生活，留学生需要学习中文。
EN: To adapt to life in China, foreign students need to learn Chinese.

ZH: 我们在学校成立了一个留学生交流俱乐部。
EN: We have established a foreign student exchange club at school.

ZH: 许多留学生选择在中国留学一段时间。
EN: Many foreign students choose to study in China for a period of time.

ZH: 留学生们在寒假期间返回自己的国家度假。
EN: Foreign students return to their own countries for vacation during winter break.

ZH: 留学生宿舍有专门的厨房供他们做饭。
EN: The foreign student dormitory has a dedicated kitchen for them to cook.

ZH: 学校为留学生提供了英语辅导课程。
EN: The school provides English tutoring courses for foreign students.

ZH: 大部分留学生选择在海外深造。
EN: The majority of foreign students choose to pursue further studies abroad.

ZH: 留学生常常组织国际文化展览活动。
EN: Foreign students often organize international cultural exhibitions.

ZH: 我的邻居是一名留学生，来自德国。
EN: My neighbor is a foreign student from Germany.

ZH: 留学生们在课余时间经常一起学习和交流。
EN: Foreign students often study and socialize together in their spare time.

ZH: 学校图书馆有一块专门为留学生留出的学习区域。
EN: The school library has a designated study area for foreign students.

ZH: 留学生可以申请校外住宿，和中国学生一起合租。
EN: Foreign students can apply for off-campus accommodation and share an apartment with Chinese students.
